1
00:01:35,000 --> 00:01:39,990
[This Thriving Land]

2
00:01:40,330 --> 00:01:42,940
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:43,350 --> 00:01:44,630
What does he mean?

4
00:01:44,650 --> 00:01:46,750
Does he really want to
marry your sister and abandon you?

5
00:01:46,750 --> 00:01:48,680
I don't want to talk about this now.

6
00:01:52,610 --> 00:01:53,090
Xiu.

7
00:01:54,450 --> 00:01:55,680
Tell me the truth.

8
00:01:57,320 --> 00:01:59,580
You still care about Fei Wendian, right?

9
00:02:02,130 --> 00:02:02,970
He and I...

10
00:02:04,400 --> 00:02:06,140
It's impossible between us.

11
00:02:06,280 --> 00:02:07,730
I've given up.

12
00:02:07,730 --> 00:02:10,130
I don't understand those twists and turns.

13
00:02:11,090 --> 00:02:12,090
And I don't know

14
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,730
what it means to give up.

15
00:02:14,010 --> 00:02:15,750
All I know is that if you like someone,
then just go all out for him.

16
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:17,680
If you don't like him,
then just forget about him.

17
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:20,079
You can't be vague
and ambiguous like this.

18
00:02:21,650 --> 00:02:22,560
Dajiao.

19
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:24,720
These days,

20
00:02:25,650 --> 00:02:27,720
I've heard

21
00:02:28,530 --> 00:02:29,600
and seen it all,

22
00:02:30,050 --> 00:02:32,490
whether I should've or not.

23
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:40,810
I really want to leave this village.

24
00:02:43,530 --> 00:02:44,860
But I really have no idea

25
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,880
where to go right now.

26
00:02:52,940 --> 00:02:54,600
If you don't want to keep me...

27
00:02:55,490 --> 00:02:56,820
I'm willing to keep you!

28
00:03:00,470 --> 00:03:01,800
I'm willing to keep you.

29
00:03:03,560 --> 00:03:04,820
But you and Fei Wendian

30
00:03:06,050 --> 00:03:08,310
have been that close since you were kids.

31
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:11,560
Can you just ignore him

32
00:03:12,490 --> 00:03:13,650
and leave like that?

33
00:03:14,160 --> 00:03:14,970
I know.

34
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,720
If Fei Wendian

35
00:03:17,329 --> 00:03:19,060
hadn't continued his studies,

36
00:03:19,810 --> 00:03:21,940
you would have got married 3 years ago.

37
00:03:24,930 --> 00:03:25,530
Xiu.

38
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,680
Tell me the truth.

39
00:03:30,490 --> 00:03:32,220
Do you still want to be with him?

40
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:35,810
It's meaningless

41
00:03:38,000 --> 00:03:39,260
to talk about this now.

42
00:03:41,120 --> 00:03:41,880
Last night,

43
00:03:42,770 --> 00:03:44,500
you were talking in your sleep.

44
00:03:45,650 --> 00:03:47,530
You kept calling his name.

45
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:50,440
I know

46
00:03:51,650 --> 00:03:52,710
you still like him.

47
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,940
You're too embarrassed to ask

48
00:03:57,090 --> 00:03:58,220
what he's thinking,

49
00:03:58,370 --> 00:03:59,770
and you don't want to ask,

50
00:04:00,680 --> 00:04:01,890
then I'll ask for you.

51
00:04:03,000 --> 00:04:03,560
Xiu.

52
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,880
Your father didn't redeem you.

53
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,610
I understand you're mad at him.

54
00:04:07,970 --> 00:04:09,230
Why does the Fei family

55
00:04:09,330 --> 00:04:10,860
have nothing to do with you?

56
00:04:11,210 --> 00:04:12,070
I'll go ask him.

57
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,600
I want to know
what Fei Wendian is thinking.

58
00:04:14,970 --> 00:04:15,650
Wait for me!

59
00:04:16,089 --> 00:04:16,790
Dajiao.

60
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,450
Fei Wendian!

61
00:04:56,970 --> 00:04:58,170
I was looking for you.

62
00:05:00,410 --> 00:05:01,240
Feng Dajiao.

63
00:05:02,240 --> 00:05:02,650
I...

64
00:05:02,650 --> 00:05:03,530
What?

65
00:05:04,590 --> 00:05:06,840
The Ning family didn't care about Xiuxiu.

66
00:05:06,840 --> 00:05:08,970
Why didn't you redeem her and save her?

67
00:05:09,090 --> 00:05:10,530
You even married her sister!

68
00:05:10,530 --> 00:05:11,790
What are you thinking?

69
00:05:13,130 --> 00:05:15,530
Many things aren't
what you think they are.

70
00:05:17,290 --> 00:05:18,900
Susu and I are innocent.

71
00:05:20,130 --> 00:05:21,840
But it was my fault that day.

72
00:05:23,090 --> 00:05:24,820
I shouldn't have drunk so much.

73
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:27,360
I didn't see the situation clearly,

74
00:05:27,650 --> 00:05:29,510
and delayed the rescue of Xiuxiu.

75
00:05:32,450 --> 00:05:34,090
Xiuxiu has married you.

76
00:05:35,840 --> 00:05:37,330
You must treat her well.

77
00:05:39,210 --> 00:05:39,940
Stand there!

78
00:05:45,770 --> 00:05:46,570
Let me ask you.

79
00:05:47,840 --> 00:05:49,210
Do you like Xiuxiu?

80
00:05:53,190 --> 00:05:54,790
What difference does it make

81
00:05:54,890 --> 00:05:56,400
if I like her or not?

82
00:05:56,890 --> 00:05:58,360
Now, whenever I think about

83
00:05:58,360 --> 00:06:01,360
the humiliation she suffered
in the bandits' lair...

84
00:06:06,690 --> 00:06:07,420
Fei Wendian!

85
00:06:07,890 --> 00:06:09,360
Are you still a man?

86
00:06:11,130 --> 00:06:12,400
Is it Xiuxiu's fault

87
00:06:12,720 --> 00:06:14,050
that she was kidnapped?

88
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:16,620
It's your fault that you didn't save her.

89
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:17,920
It's your fault.

90
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,650
How dare you cry?

91
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:25,530
I don't know how to face Xiuxiu now.

92
00:06:42,530 --> 00:06:43,280
Do you

93
00:06:44,570 --> 00:06:46,100
still want to marry Xiuxiu?

94
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,159
Doesn't she hate me?

95
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:55,130
Will she still go with me?

96
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:56,330
Well...

97
00:06:57,570 --> 00:06:58,570
I'll tell her.

98
00:06:59,650 --> 00:07:00,850
She's at my house now.

99
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,920
But you have to

100
00:07:03,280 --> 00:07:05,240
pick her up before noon.

101
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,330
Dajiao.

102
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:13,180
But you can't go empty-handed.

103
00:07:14,090 --> 00:07:15,160
You can't

104
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,960
just take Xiuxiu away like this,

105
00:07:17,280 --> 00:07:18,740
without any explanation.

106
00:07:19,240 --> 00:07:21,040
People will gossip about her.

107
00:07:22,090 --> 00:07:23,890
We can't let her suffer anymore.

108
00:07:25,330 --> 00:07:26,570
What should I do?

109
00:07:27,030 --> 00:07:29,230
You must treat it like a formal wedding,

110
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:30,920
hire a big sedan chair

111
00:07:31,210 --> 00:07:32,659
and a group of trumpeters

112
00:07:33,159 --> 00:07:35,330
to pick up Xiuxiu with drums and gongs.

113
00:07:35,970 --> 00:07:37,210
Then you have to parade around the village

114
00:07:37,210 --> 00:07:38,240
three times

115
00:07:39,090 --> 00:07:40,820
so that everyone in the village

116
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:42,430
knows that no matter what,

117
00:07:43,280 --> 00:07:44,360
you, Fei Wendian,

118
00:07:45,010 --> 00:07:47,340
have married Ning Xiuxiu in a grand manner

119
00:07:47,530 --> 00:07:48,730
and cleared her name.

120
00:07:49,450 --> 00:07:50,130
Okay.

121
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:51,840
Okay.

122
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,360
I'll go home now.

123
00:07:53,690 --> 00:07:54,720
I'll hire a sedan chair.

124
00:07:54,720 --> 00:07:55,850
I'll pick up Xiuxiu.

125
00:08:07,840 --> 00:08:09,130
So I

126
00:08:09,890 --> 00:08:12,210
gave Xiuxiu back to Fei Wendian again.

127
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:15,280
I'm heartbroken,

128
00:08:16,040 --> 00:08:17,720
but now I'm the only one

129
00:08:18,730 --> 00:08:20,770
who can protect her.

130
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,690
The meat is not bad.

131
00:08:34,210 --> 00:08:36,450
Streaky pork, really good.

132
00:08:36,450 --> 00:08:37,169
Look.

133
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,120
What a pity.

134
00:08:39,690 --> 00:08:41,330
It's better to be fattier.

135
00:08:41,380 --> 00:08:43,380
No, it's great.

136
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,520
Hurry up.

137
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,800
Chop the meat and make porridge.

138
00:08:52,220 --> 00:08:53,690
This meat

139
00:08:54,880 --> 00:08:56,240
is worth 15 mu of land.

140
00:08:57,700 --> 00:08:58,500
It's worth it.

141
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,640
I saw Fei Wendian.

142
00:09:03,640 --> 00:09:05,050
Didn't I tell you? He and I...

143
00:09:05,050 --> 00:09:06,760
It's not what you think, Xiu.

144
00:09:07,570 --> 00:09:08,410
I think

145
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:09,640
there must be some misunderstanding

146
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:10,910
between you and Fei Wendian,

147
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:12,640
but I can't explain it clearly.

148
00:09:12,720 --> 00:09:14,330
He'll explain it to you

149
00:09:14,330 --> 00:09:15,600
when he sees you.

150
00:09:15,720 --> 00:09:17,090
But most importantly,

151
00:09:17,520 --> 00:09:19,360
Fei Wendian has hired a sedan chair

152
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,930
and a group of drummers and gong players.

153
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:22,220
He will pick you up

154
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,360
before noon

155
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,760
and take you to the Fei family.

156
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:25,330
Also,

157
00:09:25,690 --> 00:09:26,600
I told him

158
00:09:26,880 --> 00:09:27,930
to take you

159
00:09:28,170 --> 00:09:29,900
around the village three times

160
00:09:30,410 --> 00:09:31,760
to make up for
all the suffering you've endured.

161
00:09:31,760 --> 00:09:33,120
Will he really come?

162
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:35,170
Yes.

163
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,360
He promised me.

164
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,790
Dajiao.

165
00:09:50,430 --> 00:09:52,310
Come eat with Xiuxiu.

166
00:09:52,660 --> 00:09:53,990
The meal is ready.

167
00:09:54,410 --> 00:09:55,880
Today is meat porridge.

168
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,090
Come and eat.

169
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:00,060
Coming.

170
00:10:05,970 --> 00:10:06,760
Have some.

171
00:10:07,720 --> 00:10:08,570
Fill yourself

172
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:10,820
and then you can take the sedan chair.

173
00:10:11,120 --> 00:10:11,980
I'm not hungry.

174
00:10:13,930 --> 00:10:14,990
I'll get it for you.

175
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:29,480
Wendian, I'm looking for you.

176
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,930
Have you found a way to send me home?

177
00:10:30,930 --> 00:10:31,450
Susu.

178
00:10:31,620 --> 00:10:32,500
Wait for me.

179
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,580
I have a way to solve your problem.

180
00:10:34,760 --> 00:10:35,360
Really?

181
00:10:35,360 --> 00:10:37,020
You really have a way to send me home?

182
00:10:37,020 --> 00:10:37,780
Trust me.

183
00:10:38,040 --> 00:10:39,900
I will definitely let you go home.

184
00:10:50,290 --> 00:10:51,000
Have some.

185
00:10:51,640 --> 00:10:52,500
Meat porridge.

186
00:10:56,480 --> 00:10:57,610
Will Fei Wendian...

187
00:10:58,840 --> 00:10:59,970
really come?

188
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:01,880
He promised me

189
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:02,850
he would come.

190
00:11:04,450 --> 00:11:05,170
Have some.

191
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,050
What did you say?

192
00:11:08,760 --> 00:11:09,600
Feng Dajiao

193
00:11:09,790 --> 00:11:11,760
asked you to bring Xiuxiu back

194
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:14,480
and hire a sedan chair
to go around the village three times?

195
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:15,240
Yes, Sister-in-law.

196
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,810
We have to do it this way.

197
00:11:16,830 --> 00:11:19,560
And I'm going to
pick her up personally this time.

198
00:11:21,470 --> 00:11:22,730
You went to see Xiuxiu?

199
00:11:22,810 --> 00:11:23,330
Yes.

200
00:11:23,540 --> 00:11:25,390
I ran into Dajiao
when I was looking for Xiuxiu.

201
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:27,650
He asked me to pick up Xiuxiu before noon.

202
00:11:30,050 --> 00:11:31,850
If you really bring Xiuxiu back,

203
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,800
I'll be too ashamed to see

204
00:11:34,950 --> 00:11:36,720
the ancestors of the Fei family.

205
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,810
Sister-in-law,

206
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,050
it was you

207
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,720
who arranged the marriage
between me and Xiuxiu,

208
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,290
and you've watched us

209
00:11:42,290 --> 00:11:43,890
stay in love all these years.

210
00:11:43,930 --> 00:11:45,140
You know

211
00:11:45,160 --> 00:11:47,590
how important Xiuxiu is to me.

212
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:50,170
Xiuxiu voluntarily married Feng Dajiao.

213
00:11:50,170 --> 00:11:51,690
Everyone in the village saw it.

214
00:11:51,690 --> 00:11:53,930
She walked into the door
of the Feng family herself.

215
00:11:53,930 --> 00:11:56,130
What reason do you have to go pick her up?

216
00:11:56,270 --> 00:11:57,910
Wendian, this is fate,

217
00:11:58,000 --> 00:11:58,970
the fate of Xiuxiu.

218
00:11:58,970 --> 00:11:59,480
Yes.

219
00:11:59,880 --> 00:12:00,720
Sister-in-law,

220
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:01,600
you're right.

221
00:12:01,810 --> 00:12:03,940
What's happened to Xiuxiu is her fate.

222
00:12:04,710 --> 00:12:05,840
But I have to tell you

223
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:07,810
Xiuxiu's fate

224
00:12:08,050 --> 00:12:09,210
is mine,

225
00:12:09,210 --> 00:12:10,330
and I refuse to submit to it,

226
00:12:10,330 --> 00:12:11,330
nor will I let her

227
00:12:11,330 --> 00:12:12,880
be defeated by it.

228
00:12:15,890 --> 00:12:17,220
Sister-in-law, you...

229
00:12:19,090 --> 00:12:21,040
You can disregard my dignity,

230
00:12:21,650 --> 00:12:23,020
the Fei family's honor,

231
00:12:23,090 --> 00:12:25,090
and even the teachings of our ancestors.

232
00:12:25,090 --> 00:12:27,520
But can you think about it?

233
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,360
Do you think those lowly farmers

234
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,720
aren't scheming?

235
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:34,050
Feng Er is crazy for land.

236
00:12:34,170 --> 00:12:36,930
He proposed to the Ning family
just for Xiuxiu's dowry.

237
00:12:36,930 --> 00:12:38,210
Never did he expect

238
00:12:38,210 --> 00:12:39,930
she'd refuse it.

239
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,970
Now they have come to their senses

240
00:12:43,970 --> 00:12:45,360
and realised that Xiuxiu cannot stay,

241
00:12:45,360 --> 00:12:47,220
so they asked you to bring her back

242
00:12:47,720 --> 00:12:49,480
and had you carry her around the village

243
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,080
three times on a sedan chair.

244
00:12:51,520 --> 00:12:53,720
They really put a lot of thought into it.

245
00:12:56,570 --> 00:12:57,500
Sister-in-law,

246
00:12:58,090 --> 00:12:59,410
what do you mean?

247
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:01,360
The Feng family doesn't want her anymore,

248
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:02,880
nor does Feng Dajiao.

249
00:13:03,570 --> 00:13:05,830
Who would want a woman like her, Wendian?

250
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:08,690
Go ask anyone on the street.

251
00:13:09,030 --> 00:13:10,750
Who'd marry a woman abused by

252
00:13:10,780 --> 00:13:11,480
so many bandits?

253
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:12,410
Sister-in-law!

254
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:21,410
Put your hand on your chest

255
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:22,840
and ask yourself.

256
00:13:23,240 --> 00:13:24,770
Are you sure you don't mind?

257
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:26,720
Are you sure you wouldn't mind

258
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:29,050
if Xiuxiu were carrying a bandit's child?

259
00:13:29,930 --> 00:13:31,480
I'm telling you today.

260
00:13:31,970 --> 00:13:33,480
If you truly don't mind

261
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:36,810
and can carry her in a sedan chair,
parading three times around the village,

262
00:13:36,810 --> 00:13:38,340
I'll arrange your wedding!

263
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:45,480
Go in.

264
00:13:46,330 --> 00:13:47,970
Go in and tell the ancestors

265
00:13:48,330 --> 00:13:50,060
if you want to take this person.

266
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,290
After that,

267
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:53,330
decide for yourself

268
00:13:54,050 --> 00:13:55,250
if you still want her.

269
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:32,220
I'm very anxious,

270
00:14:32,980 --> 00:14:36,710
even more so than the first time
I waited at home for the sedan chair.

271
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:41,150
Will Wendian really come to marry me?

272
00:14:43,000 --> 00:14:44,510
Mrs. Fei said

273
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:48,730
the Fei family wouldn't want
a woman abused by bandits.

274
00:14:50,080 --> 00:14:50,960
Is he

275
00:14:52,200 --> 00:14:53,660
really going to abandon me

276
00:14:54,210 --> 00:14:55,850
and keep Susu?

277
00:15:07,630 --> 00:15:08,800
When we meet,

278
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:12,430
I must get to the bottom of these matters.

279
00:15:13,440 --> 00:15:14,680
But that day,

280
00:15:16,320 --> 00:15:18,350
I waited for a long time.

281
00:15:19,930 --> 00:15:21,780
He didn't come to pick me up.

282
00:15:55,190 --> 00:15:55,980
Madam.

283
00:15:57,030 --> 00:15:57,670
Come in.

284
00:16:06,790 --> 00:16:07,460
Madam.

285
00:16:14,980 --> 00:16:16,340
Do something for me.

286
00:16:21,460 --> 00:16:22,980
It's past noon.

