566
00:33:25,740 --> 00:33:27,330
What did you do, Xiu?

567
00:33:29,700 --> 00:33:31,200
I just wanted to get up early

568
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:32,860
to make breakfast for you all.

569
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:35,850
But I couldn't find
the millet and white rice.

570
00:33:36,190 --> 00:33:37,190
Are you all right?

571
00:33:38,230 --> 00:33:40,770
Mother, Xiuxiu threw
a whole armful of firewood

572
00:33:40,770 --> 00:33:42,010
into the stove.

573
00:33:42,220 --> 00:33:44,460
No wonder the smoke and flames got so big.

574
00:33:44,460 --> 00:33:46,060
I couldn't find any matches,

575
00:33:46,090 --> 00:33:47,620
only the chestnut flower braids.

576
00:33:47,620 --> 00:33:49,140
I finally managed to light it,

577
00:33:49,140 --> 00:33:49,940
but I was afraid the fire would go out,

578
00:33:49,940 --> 00:33:51,600
so I threw all the firewood in.

579
00:33:51,950 --> 00:33:53,160
It's not your fault.

580
00:33:53,180 --> 00:33:55,740
You don't cook at home, do you?

581
00:33:55,760 --> 00:33:56,560
In our family,

582
00:33:57,140 --> 00:33:59,460
we always use chestnut flower braids
to light the stove.

583
00:33:59,460 --> 00:34:01,320
We don't have any matches at home.

584
00:34:01,630 --> 00:34:03,630
Don't worry. I'll teach you slowly.

585
00:34:04,980 --> 00:34:06,040
No need to teach me.

586
00:34:06,190 --> 00:34:07,720
Just tell me and that'll do.

587
00:34:08,880 --> 00:34:10,120
Dajiao's wife.

588
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:13,190
You don't have to do
this kind of work anymore.

589
00:34:13,190 --> 00:34:14,560
If you want to do something,

590
00:34:14,560 --> 00:34:15,960
do something important.

591
00:34:17,739 --> 00:34:19,260
What do you mean by that?

592
00:34:21,780 --> 00:34:23,090
You don't know?

593
00:34:23,090 --> 00:34:24,130
Let me tell you.

594
00:34:24,469 --> 00:34:27,679
Go home and ask your father for the land.

595
00:34:27,909 --> 00:34:30,020
Bring me the deed

596
00:34:30,310 --> 00:34:32,780
to the 15 mu of land.

597
00:34:36,570 --> 00:34:37,770
I don't have a father.

598
00:34:37,870 --> 00:34:39,400
How could you say that?

599
00:34:39,530 --> 00:34:40,650
You don't have a father?

600
00:34:40,650 --> 00:34:42,690
Were you born out of a stone?

601
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:44,340
You can't say you have no parents.

602
00:34:44,340 --> 00:34:45,530
I don't have a father,

603
00:34:45,530 --> 00:34:47,730
and I don't want that lousy land either.

604
00:34:47,850 --> 00:34:48,810
Lousy land?

605
00:34:50,010 --> 00:34:51,980
It might seem lousy to you,

606
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:54,420
but to us farmers,

607
00:34:54,420 --> 00:34:55,820
it's our lifeline!

608
00:34:56,170 --> 00:34:58,260
We depend on this land to survive!

609
00:34:58,980 --> 00:35:01,480
Your father only gave 15 mu of land,
which isn't much,

610
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:04,250
but I accepted it because of you.

611
00:35:06,780 --> 00:35:07,850
Whether you accept it or not

612
00:35:07,850 --> 00:35:09,250
has nothing to do with me.

613
00:35:09,820 --> 00:35:10,740
In my eyes,

614
00:35:11,450 --> 00:35:13,310
that land is nothing but trouble.

615
00:35:13,430 --> 00:35:14,710
It's a death warrant.

616
00:35:16,110 --> 00:35:16,970
I don't want it.

617
00:35:18,640 --> 00:35:19,890
How could she say that?

618
00:35:19,890 --> 00:35:21,150
How could she say that?

619
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:23,800
Can you stop talking about that land?

620
00:35:24,060 --> 00:35:27,230
If we don't talk about the land,
what else is there to talk about?

621
00:35:27,230 --> 00:35:29,430
Are we just going to
sweep this matter under the rug?

622
00:35:29,430 --> 00:35:31,960
Take it easy. Give her some time.

623
00:35:32,330 --> 00:35:33,580
What's the point of waiting?

624
00:35:33,580 --> 00:35:35,660
What if her puffy-eyed father

625
00:35:35,690 --> 00:35:36,780
changes his mind?

626
00:35:36,780 --> 00:35:38,490
It's no use arguing about it.

627
00:35:39,180 --> 00:35:40,860
It depends on Xiuxiu.

628
00:35:44,190 --> 00:35:46,390
You little brat! You're defending her!

629
00:35:58,610 --> 00:36:00,010
Is it true that if I want to

630
00:36:03,530 --> 00:36:05,610
live peacefully in the Feng family,

631
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:09,760
I have to take that land?

632
00:36:11,920 --> 00:36:13,920
You won't go back to the Ning family;

633
00:36:14,130 --> 00:36:15,530
you won't acknowledge your father;

634
00:36:15,530 --> 00:36:17,330
and you don't want any of his things.

635
00:36:17,330 --> 00:36:18,590
I understand all that.

636
00:36:19,420 --> 00:36:22,820
You can't force someone
to do something they don't want to do.

637
00:36:24,070 --> 00:36:25,940
If my father brings up that land again,

638
00:36:25,940 --> 00:36:27,740
just tell him to come to me for it.

639
00:36:30,650 --> 00:36:31,300
Dajiao!

640
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:33,050
Dajiao!

641
00:36:33,910 --> 00:36:34,500
Dajiao!

642
00:36:35,900 --> 00:36:36,650
Dajiao!

643
00:36:37,630 --> 00:36:38,050
Zhuzi.

644
00:36:38,050 --> 00:36:39,460
Hurry up!

645
00:36:39,460 --> 00:36:40,260
What's wrong?

646
00:36:40,450 --> 00:36:41,700
My cow is sick.

647
00:36:41,730 --> 00:36:42,610
Hurry up and come with me!

648
00:36:42,610 --> 00:36:43,140
Let's go.

649
00:36:54,420 --> 00:36:55,900
Xiuxiu, are you inside?

650
00:37:03,210 --> 00:37:04,170
Xiuxiu.

651
00:37:05,170 --> 00:37:07,780
Dajiao's father is just like that.

652
00:37:08,780 --> 00:37:10,570
He's completely obsessed

653
00:37:10,650 --> 00:37:12,170
with land.

654
00:37:12,380 --> 00:37:14,050
Don't take it to heart.

655
00:37:15,130 --> 00:37:17,170
We'll talk to him about it later.

656
00:37:19,170 --> 00:37:21,050
I forgot why I came here.

657
00:37:22,010 --> 00:37:24,130
I want to make you a pair of shoes,

658
00:37:24,130 --> 00:37:25,380
a pair of cotton-padded shoes.

659
00:37:25,380 --> 00:37:26,650
I'll make

660
00:37:26,650 --> 00:37:28,210
whatever you like.

661
00:37:29,820 --> 00:37:31,480
Just make it the same as yours.

662
00:37:31,900 --> 00:37:32,860
That won't do.

663
00:37:33,080 --> 00:37:35,480
I only make shoes
for Dajiao and his father.

664
00:37:35,510 --> 00:37:36,990
I don't have your size.

665
00:37:37,630 --> 00:37:39,370
Let me measure your foot.

666
00:37:39,390 --> 00:37:40,390
Sit down.

667
00:37:42,570 --> 00:37:44,780
After I take your measurements,
I'll head over to Granny Zheng’s.

668
00:37:44,780 --> 00:37:47,010
She has many shoe patterns.

669
00:37:47,010 --> 00:37:49,260
All the young girls
and married women in our village

670
00:37:49,260 --> 00:37:50,920
go to her to get shoe patterns.

671
00:37:51,060 --> 00:37:51,940
Come on.

672
00:37:52,420 --> 00:37:53,420
I'll do it myself.

673
00:37:57,490 --> 00:37:59,260
Make a pair of warm and nice shoes

674
00:37:59,260 --> 00:38:00,590
to wear for the New Year.

675
00:38:03,690 --> 00:38:04,730
My goodness!

676
00:38:05,320 --> 00:38:06,430
Look at your foot!

677
00:38:06,510 --> 00:38:09,410
It's really pretty!

678
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:12,900
Let me sketch this part again.

679
00:38:14,320 --> 00:38:15,680
And one more touch here.

680
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:18,910
All right.

681
00:38:18,930 --> 00:38:20,960
Put it on. Don't catch a cold.

682
00:38:22,690 --> 00:38:23,610
Thank you.

683
00:38:24,820 --> 00:38:26,900
Don't mention it. We're family.

684
00:38:27,900 --> 00:38:31,030
I'm happy to make a pair of shoes
for my daughter-in-law.

685
00:38:31,040 --> 00:38:32,520
You are so nice to me.

686
00:38:33,140 --> 00:38:34,540
We are all family now.

687
00:38:34,610 --> 00:38:36,860
Don't always say "thank you".

688
00:38:36,890 --> 00:38:38,160
I'm not an outsider.

689
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:40,440
Take your time. I'm leaving.

690
00:38:43,220 --> 00:38:45,410
Your feet look pretty.

691
00:38:45,890 --> 00:38:47,210
My goodness.

692
00:38:56,090 --> 00:38:56,860
Mother!

693
00:38:57,280 --> 00:38:58,400
I'm back!

694
00:38:58,570 --> 00:38:59,130
Mother!

695
00:38:59,820 --> 00:39:00,860
You're back?

696
00:39:00,860 --> 00:39:01,860
Don't kick me out.

697
00:39:02,240 --> 00:39:03,900
I've discussed with Mrs. Fei.

698
00:39:03,980 --> 00:39:05,260
Wendian personally sent me back.

699
00:39:05,260 --> 00:39:07,260
I mean, what took you so long?

700
00:39:08,420 --> 00:39:09,260
Susu!

701
00:39:09,260 --> 00:39:09,770
Sister-in-law.

702
00:39:09,770 --> 00:39:11,000
You are so beautiful!

703
00:39:11,170 --> 00:39:12,260
You look like

704
00:39:12,260 --> 00:39:13,560
a whole new person with this outfit!

705
00:39:13,560 --> 00:39:14,760
The fabric is so good.

706
00:39:15,290 --> 00:39:16,300
Is it from Hangzhou?

707
00:39:16,300 --> 00:39:17,450
Mrs. Fei gave it to me.

708
00:39:17,450 --> 00:39:18,940
I didn't want to wear it,
but she insisted.

709
00:39:18,940 --> 00:39:20,170
And this pearl hairpin.

710
00:39:20,170 --> 00:39:21,090
She pulled it from her own head

711
00:39:21,090 --> 00:39:22,970
and put it on me when I was leaving.

712
00:39:24,170 --> 00:39:25,380
Mrs. Fei

713
00:39:25,610 --> 00:39:26,810
really went out of her way

714
00:39:26,810 --> 00:39:27,980
and treated you well.

715
00:39:27,980 --> 00:39:29,240
Wendian, you're here!

716
00:39:29,340 --> 00:39:30,140
Hello, Uncle.

717
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:32,030
What uncle?

718
00:39:32,250 --> 00:39:33,460
You should change the way you address him.

719
00:39:33,460 --> 00:39:34,590
I'll go find Mother.

720
00:39:35,950 --> 00:39:37,550
Brother-in-law. Come on in!

721
00:39:43,740 --> 00:39:45,740
Master! Master! Master!

722
00:39:49,010 --> 00:39:49,740
It was sent by

723
00:39:50,120 --> 00:39:51,920
Steward Liu from the Fei family.

724
00:40:03,610 --> 00:40:04,380
Mother.

725
00:40:05,380 --> 00:40:06,420
I'm back.

726
00:40:07,610 --> 00:40:09,260
Xiuxiu is back?

727
00:40:10,050 --> 00:40:10,650
Mother.

728
00:40:11,010 --> 00:40:12,210
I'm Susu.

729
00:40:15,860 --> 00:40:16,820
Susu.

730
00:40:17,940 --> 00:40:19,340
How did you get back here?

731
00:40:19,740 --> 00:40:21,570
Wendian sent me back.

732
00:40:22,170 --> 00:40:23,210
Mr. Fei.

733
00:40:24,380 --> 00:40:25,380
Good boy.

734
00:40:26,940 --> 00:40:29,140
The Ning family is to blame for this.

735
00:40:31,050 --> 00:40:31,780
Aunt,

736
00:40:32,050 --> 00:40:33,610
now that things have come to this,

737
00:40:33,610 --> 00:40:34,940
no one is to blame.

738
00:40:36,050 --> 00:40:37,260
It's just fate.

739
00:40:38,520 --> 00:40:40,650
You need to take good care of yourself.

740
00:40:47,260 --> 00:40:47,900
Uncle.

741
00:40:48,520 --> 00:40:49,210
Aunt.

742
00:40:50,300 --> 00:40:52,300
These past few days,
Susu has been staying at my house,

743
00:40:52,300 --> 00:40:54,230
and we've treated her like a guest,

744
00:40:54,490 --> 00:40:56,690
not daring to make the slightest mistake.

745
00:40:56,690 --> 00:40:58,260
However, because Susu and I

746
00:40:58,530 --> 00:40:59,690
have never had

747
00:40:59,690 --> 00:41:01,380
an arranged marriage,

748
00:41:01,690 --> 00:41:02,980
my sister-in-law asked me

749
00:41:02,980 --> 00:41:04,380
to bring Susu back today.

750
00:41:05,610 --> 00:41:06,170
Aunt,

751
00:41:06,610 --> 00:41:08,610
Susu and I are completely innocent.

752
00:41:13,260 --> 00:41:14,860
Mrs. Fei is so thoughtful.

753
00:41:15,340 --> 00:41:16,600
You don't know, do you?

754
00:41:17,280 --> 00:41:18,880
Mrs. Fei even sent a message.

755
00:41:19,170 --> 00:41:19,900
What is it?

756
00:41:20,180 --> 00:41:21,180
Mrs. Fei

757
00:41:21,530 --> 00:41:22,900
sent back both

758
00:41:22,900 --> 00:41:24,260
our dowry list

759
00:41:24,260 --> 00:41:25,900
and your betrothal gift list,

760
00:41:25,900 --> 00:41:28,420
saying that the Fei family
can forgo all of these

761
00:41:28,420 --> 00:41:30,050
except for the 50 mu of land.

762
00:41:30,460 --> 00:41:31,660
Since Susu is already

763
00:41:32,170 --> 00:41:34,230
a daughter-in-law of the Fei family,

764
00:41:34,610 --> 00:41:37,010
if she breaks off the marriage
and remarries,

765
00:41:37,010 --> 00:41:40,870
she would need several times
the amount of dowry to get married again.

766
00:41:40,980 --> 00:41:42,240
These betrothal gifts

767
00:41:42,530 --> 00:41:44,460
can be considered as a gift to Susu.

768
00:41:47,530 --> 00:41:50,650
What? What does Mrs. Fei mean?

769
00:41:50,900 --> 00:41:52,650
What's wrong with your family?

770
00:41:52,730 --> 00:41:54,370
This is a ridiculous matter.

771
00:41:54,760 --> 00:41:55,920
Sending Susu back

772
00:41:56,530 --> 00:41:57,770
is only right and proper.

773
00:41:57,770 --> 00:42:00,450
But Susu is already your wife.

774
00:42:00,620 --> 00:42:01,750
If you send her back,

775
00:42:01,770 --> 00:42:03,050
will she still be able to get married?

776
00:42:03,050 --> 00:42:04,670
Sister-in-law, what are you talking about?

777
00:42:04,670 --> 00:42:06,980
Father asked me
to marry him for my sister.

778
00:42:06,980 --> 00:42:08,980
What? You didn't go to
rescue my sister before,

779
00:42:08,980 --> 00:42:11,170
so she married Feng Dajiao out of spite.

780
00:42:11,170 --> 00:42:13,610
Now you want to make the best
of a mistake and send me away

781
00:42:13,610 --> 00:42:14,940
so you can save yourselves
the trouble, right?

782
00:42:14,940 --> 00:42:16,600
Mother, they are bullying me!

783
00:42:17,610 --> 00:42:18,300
Come here.

784
00:42:19,390 --> 00:42:20,380
The doctor said

785
00:42:20,380 --> 00:42:22,510
if you want your mother to live longer,

786
00:42:22,590 --> 00:42:24,520
you must not let her worry anymore.

787
00:42:24,570 --> 00:42:25,610
Listen to me.

788
00:42:26,190 --> 00:42:28,100
It won't be good if you come back.

789
00:42:28,520 --> 00:42:31,080
Not to mention
the gossip of the neighbours,

790
00:42:31,290 --> 00:42:32,220
but even at home,

791
00:42:32,740 --> 00:42:33,300
things

792
00:42:33,530 --> 00:42:35,720
won't be the same as
when you were a little girl.

793
00:42:35,720 --> 00:42:36,530
How is it different?

794
00:42:36,530 --> 00:42:37,530
How can it be different?

795
00:42:37,530 --> 00:42:38,980
How can it be the same?

796
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:40,690
You've married once.

797
00:42:40,900 --> 00:42:42,300
But it wasn't my choice!

798
00:42:42,300 --> 00:42:43,820
Father deceived me!

799
00:42:43,820 --> 00:42:46,300
If I were you, I wouldn't come back.

800
00:42:46,540 --> 00:42:47,500
You stupid cow!

801
00:42:48,730 --> 00:42:49,240
Brother.

802
00:42:49,240 --> 00:42:50,320
You stupid cow!

803
00:42:50,530 --> 00:42:52,380
Who are you to talk here?

804
00:42:52,610 --> 00:42:53,090
What took you so long?

805
00:42:53,090 --> 00:42:54,530
If you keep talking nonsense,

806
00:42:54,530 --> 00:42:55,380
I'll beat you to death!

807
00:42:55,380 --> 00:42:56,820
Kejin. Kejin...

808
00:42:56,900 --> 00:42:58,300
Sister, don't be afraid.

809
00:42:58,380 --> 00:42:59,300
Come to me.

810
00:43:01,530 --> 00:43:02,650
Fei Wendian.

811
00:43:03,710 --> 00:43:05,080
You can't marry Xiuxiu.

812
00:43:06,740 --> 00:43:07,780
What? Are you

813
00:43:07,950 --> 00:43:09,430
going to keep Susu?

